quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  2,154,"Wata on wi'an …ďen wariraa…ďe fii Allah …ďen: "ko …ďe maay…ďe". Ko woni, …ďen ko wuur…ďe, kono on so'aa anndude."
  2,155,"Ma Men njarriboro on huunde, he kulol, e heege, e …óuytagol (ustogol) jawle, e woŇčkiiji, e dim…óe; Wewlin (weltin) mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen."
  2,156,"∆Āen …ďe nganndan-…óaa si musiibo he…ďii…ďe, …ďe wi'a: "Menen dey ko Allah jeyi men, pellet to makko men ruttotoo"."
  2,157,"∆Āen …óon, hino he dow ma…ď…ďe toraaje e yurmeende ummoraade ka (to ) Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko kam…ďe ngoni feewu…ďe …ďen."
  2,158,"Pellet,Safaa e Marwa ko jeyaa…óe e maandeeji [diine] Allah.Kala on hajju…óo ka suudu [Kaaba], maa o wa…ói Umra,ella woo (foo) fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji.On mo gattii mo∆ī∆īere,pellet Allah ko Jaarnoowo Anndu…óo."
  2,159,"Pellet, …ďen suu…óoo…ďe kon ko Men Jippini immorde he …ďanngannduyeeji (la…ď…ďinaa…óe) e peewal, …ďaawo nde Men ∆Āannginani …óum yim…ďe …ďen ka deftere, …ďen …óon, Allah ena Hu…óude …ďe, hu…óoo…ďe …ďen na hu…óude …ďe."
  2,160,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďe mo∆ī∆īini …ďe …ďaŇčngini: Mi Ja…ďanay …ďen …óon tuubuubuyee, ko miin woni Ja…ďoowo tuubabuya, yurmotoo…óo."
  2,161,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi ko …ďe heeferaa…ďe, …ďen …óon ena fawii…ďe ku…ódi Allah ndin e malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďen denndaangal"
  2,162,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe (saasoo…ďe) e magge. ∆Āe hayfinaŇčtaake le…ďte …óen, …ďe wonaali nennanaŇčtee…ďe (mu√Īantee…ďe)."
  2,163,"Rewetee…óo mon on ko Rewetee…óo Gooto. Rewetee…óo Alaa tanaa kanko, Jurumdeero jurmotoo…óo."